---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Tel Link
description: "a tel: hyperlink for a telephone number"
---

{% from "components/tel-link/macro.njk" import telLink %}

<h2>Common NHS numbers</h2>
<ul>
  <li>NHS 111: {{ telLink({ number: "111" }) }}</li>
  <li>Emergency: {{ telLink({ number: "999", label: "Call 999 for emergency services" }) }}</li>
  <li>NHS GP appointment line: {{ telLink({ number: "0300 123 4567" }) }}</li>
</ul>

<h2>With custom visible text</h2>
<p>{{ telLink({
  number: "0300 123 4567",
  text: "Call the surgery"
}) }}</p>

<h2>International format</h2>
<p>{{ telLink({
  number: "+44 20 7946 0958",
  text: "Call (London)"
}) }}</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The macro normalises the <code>href</code> to a dialable form
  (stripping spaces, hyphens, and parentheses), while the visible
  text preserves the formatting you supplied — so the link looks
  right and the dial still works.</p>
